1.download node.js. see https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/
2.install grunt
    npm install grunt --g
3.install webpack. 
    npm install webpack --g

4.install node_modules for grunt project
    npm install
5.cd app
6.install node_modules for vue project
    npm install

7.build webpack
    dev: npm run dev
    pro: npm run build
8.cd..
9.create nwjs app
    grunt nwjs

10.Inno Step Compiler
    setup.iss

11.over



ps. To disable the DevTools you can use chromium args in your package.json as demonstrated below:
{
    "chromium-args": "--disable-devtools"
}